"{\"uid\": \"thesouthafrican.com-sport-paris-olympics-2024-team-south-africa-kit-for-paris-olympics-2024-revealed-picture\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Copyright Blue Sky Publications (Pty) Ltd. All Rights Reserved.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 63, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 15, \"end\": 18, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sky_UK\", \"score\": 0.9346153525532186, \"rank\": 0.0465837423623677, \"text\": \"Sky\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sky_UK\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sky_UK\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"thesouthafrican.com is a division of Blue Sky Publications Ltd. Reproduction without permission prohibited  Home\\u00bbSport\\u00bbParis Olympics 2024\\u00bbTeam South Africa kit for Paris Olympics 2024 revealed - PICTURE  Sascoc and apparel partner Mr Price Sport have unveiled the kit that will be worn by the country's athletes at the Paris Olympics 2024.\", \"from\": 65, \"to\": 405, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 107, \"end\": 110, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sky_UK\", \"score\": 0.9346153525532186, \"rank\": 0.0465837423623677, \"text\": \"Sky\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sky_UK\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sky_UK\"}, {\"begin\": 204, \"end\": 221, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa_national_baseball_team\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Team South Africa\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa_national_baseball_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa_national_baseball_team\"}, {\"begin\": 230, \"end\": 244, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Paris Olympics\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 297, \"end\": 305, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mr._Price\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Mr Price\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mr._Price\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mr._Price\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Less than a week afterannouncing the first 39 athletesto representTeam South Africaat the Olympic Games in Paris in July, the South African Sports Confederation, Olympic and Paralympic Committee (Sascoc), and their apparel partner, Mr Price Sport, on Tuesday unveiled the kit that will be worn by the country's athletes at the global event.\", \"from\": 407, \"to\": 747, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 514, \"end\": 519, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.2698399488902446e-13, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The kit launch was held at the Cradle of Humankind World Heritage Site in Maropeng, in homage to the inspiration behind the designs, which feature a number of South African landmarks, as well as the natural flora and fauna found in the South African landscape.\", \"from\": 749, \"to\": 1009, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 823, \"end\": 831, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cradle_of_Humankind\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Maropeng\", \"types\": [\"Q9259\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cradle_of_Humankind\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cradle_of_Humankind\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The venue for the unveiling was equally inspired by the fact that the organisers of the Paris 2024 Games have selected a number of iconic venues for their events.\", \"from\": 1011, \"to\": 1173, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The Eiffel Tower will be the venue for beach volleyball, and the Seine River will be used for the Opening Ceremony for the Olympics, as well as the open-air swimming competition.\", \"from\": 1175, \"to\": 1353, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The Opening Ceremony for the Paralympics will be held at the Champs-Elys\\u00e9es and Place de la Concorde.\", \"from\": 1355, \"to\": 1456, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The Paralympics will be held from 28 August to 8 September, featuring 4 400 athletes in 549 events.\", \"from\": 1458, \"to\": 1557, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The Paris Olympics 2024 will be staged from 26 July to 11 August with 10 500 athletes competing across 329 events.\", \"from\": 1559, \"to\": 1673, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"WIN R2 000: Take The South African's SASSA Survey  The South African is hiring!\", \"from\": 1675, \"to\": 1754, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1675, \"end\": 1678, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/WIN_Television\", \"score\": 0.9999998246357944, \"rank\": 8.86506678507575e-08, \"text\": \"WIN\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/WIN_Television\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/WIN_Television\"}, {\"begin\": 1679, \"end\": 1681, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/DVD_region_code\", \"score\": 0.9823282698773363, \"rank\": 0.017983313191371763, \"text\": \"R2\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/DVD_region_code\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/DVD_region_code\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Freelance writing positions available  Follow The South African on Facebook for the latest local and international news  Follow The South African's WhatsApp channel for the latest sport, lifestyle and local news  Follow The South African on X for the latest, breaking news  A brand new shopping mall is coming to Pretoria East, bringing major retailers and new convenience to the area.\", \"from\": 1755, \"to\": 2140, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1903, \"end\": 1911, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/WhatsApp\", \"score\": 0.98926087